    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Family of flowering plants containing 16 genera and about 770 species, mostly in the tropics or warm temperate regions of the world. The affinities of Vitaceae have long been uncertain, with no obvious close relatives to the family</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
